{"tid":643302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港新移民數據整合 根本唔係咁差","createTime":"2018-04-26T11:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T10:45:52.000Z","uid":177244,"like":5,"dislike":99,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"af9f042ffec9560141f6eec0d3c33d7e0082cdae","tid":643302,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T11:45:48.000Z","msg":"首先 <br />\n香港人口來源 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/22498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F22498&d=3eVBHC9zzHlIoi64cOsllUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=62275746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/22498</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/26/y4jF9o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2Fy4jF9o.jpg&h=f7a1950f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/26/l2TZzx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2Fl2TZzx.jpg&h=675b23aa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/26/A7YM2j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2FA7YM2j.jpg&h=5e983fee&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港新移民來源 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2vJwF63\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2vJwF63&d=3eVBHC9zzHlIoi64cOsllUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=edef5572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2vJwF63</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/26/3e02X6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F3e02X6.jpg&h=b36fa9a9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/26/Nt6PgV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2FNt6PgV.jpg&h=c5cea576&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/26/rE6km2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2FrE6km2.jpg&h=861dd6d9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/26/9NXzcu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F9NXzcu.jpg&h=8c9f1b51&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/26/4FOfTH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F4FOfTH.jpg&h=23785648&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/26/6pHixM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F6pHixM.jpg&h=4c25413a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n新移民作為香港勞動力補充 <br />\n<br />\n新移民年齡分佈，65歲以上幾乎無 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2HYPZP9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HYPZP9&d=3eVBHC9zzHlIoi64cOsllUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=181240b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2HYPZP9</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/26/1jJY5F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F1jJY5F.jpg&h=95518100&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港勞動力短缺 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2HUb2F8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HUb2F8&d=3eVBHC9zzHlIoi64cOsllUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=417ad3f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2HUb2F8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/194410_9ff721a32e2ea8c7bbb2a77597b5ffff.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F194410_9ff721a32e2ea8c7bbb2a77597b5ffff.gif&h=ded51557&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KiESRM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit